overview: Tony is sick and tired of it. The late hours, the disrespect, his pretentious boss. He wants what's his... But what's his... Isn't his just yet. Go through his meticulous plan, step by step in how to double your capital (fast).
tagline: "Whattaya Doin' Out Here? You'll Freeze Ya Tits off!"
title: A Couple Of Regular Fellas 2
